      <h1 class="title">
      Um Guia Anarquista para o Software Livre
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    Maggio 31, 2012 0:00
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by Software Livre Brasil
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - 
  </span>

<span class="followers-count">
|
    No one following this article yet.
</span>

</span>

  <div id='article-sub-header'>
      <div id="article-hits">
